to tell me Shen Tingbai offended the Japanese

312
00:23:24,120 --> 00:23:25,320
and Kazuo Sato for me.

313
00:23:27,000 --> 00:23:28,160
Hadn't it been for him

314
00:23:28,160 --> 00:23:30,490
