324
00:23:58,320 --> 00:23:59,760
Don't you think it's ridiculous?

325
00:23:59,760 --> 00:24:00,400
But

326
00:24:00,400 --> 00:24:01,400
he is nice to you.

327
00:24:01,920 --> 00:24:03,880
Many people are nice to me.

328
00:24:03,880 --> 00:24:05,280
Should I marry them all?

329
00:24:05,680 --> 00:24:07,440
Then who do you want now?

330
00:24:14,400 --> 00:24:15,840
I don't know it either.

331
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:21,920
Maybe

