I really like yet.

334
00:24:28,760 --> 00:24:30,960
But at least I know what I want

335
00:24:31,080 --> 00:24:32,280
and what I don't want.

336
00:24:32,320 --> 00:24:33,160
I know what I like

337
00:24:33,160 --> 00:24:34,360
and what I don't like.

338
00:24:35,440 --> 00:24:36,880
I don't need what I don't want

339
00:24:36,880 --> 00:24:38,740
and I can't like what I don't like.

340
00:24:38,840 --> 00:24:40,840
Why do they have to force me to marry?

341
00:24:42,600 --> 00:24:44,000
No one can force me to do it

342
00:24:46,600 --> 00:24:47,530
