345
00:25:06,760 --> 00:25:08,160
I'm going to see a friend.

346
00:25:08,160 --> 00:25:08,820
Stop there.

347
00:25:11,360 --> 00:25:12,000
Manting

348
00:25:12,240 --> 00:25:13,440
