362
00:25:43,960 --> 00:25:44,280
You!

363
00:25:45,680 --> 00:25:46,240
Manting!

364
00:25:46,320 --> 00:25:47,980
Apologize to your father now.

365
00:25:48,160 --> 00:25:49,800
Do you still remember who you are?

366
00:25:49,800 --> 00:25:51,400
You could've been a lady

367
