378
00:26:10,360 --> 00:26:11,720
- You spoiled brat! - Manting!

379
00:26:11,720 --> 00:26:12,380
Ignore her.

380
00:26:12,560 --> 00:26:13,560
Let her go!

381
00:26:16,080 --> 00:26:17,480
Calm down.

382
00:26:17,960 --> 00:26:18,840
Don't be mad.

383
00:26:19,240 --> 00:26:20,500
Take care of yourself.

384
00:26:26,960 --> 00:26:27,520
Manting!

385
00:26:29,840 --> 00:26:30,970
Where are you going?

386
00:26:46,160 --> 00:26:47,080
Enough.

387
00:26:49,040 --> 00:26:50,640
