392
00:26:59,640 --> 00:27:00,600
Don't worry.

393
00:27:01,280 --> 00:27:02,940
You're really narcissistic.

394
00:27:04,320 --> 00:27:04,960
Xiaojun

395
00:27:08,080 --> 00:27:09,740
sometimes I really think that

396
00:27:11,840 --> 00:27:13,600
only Manzhu is their daughter

397
00:27:15,800 --> 00:27:16,520
I'm not.

398
00:27:18,440 --> 00:27:19,300
