00:29:21,200 --> 00:29:21,800
What's up?

454
00:29:22,160 --> 00:29:23,560
Keep an eye on Qu Manting for me.

455
00:29:23,560 --> 00:29:24,480
Don't let her drink anymore.

456
00:29:24,480 --> 00:29:25,600
I'll go out for a while.

457
00:29:25,600 --> 00:29:26,680
