528
00:34:23,120 --> 00:34:24,580
But it is a beautiful name.

529
00:34:25,230 --> 00:34:25,840
Really?

530
00:34:28,360 --> 00:34:29,150
This is my friend

531
00:34:29,150 --> 00:34:29,880
Tan Xiaojun.

532
00:34:30,280 --> 00:34:30,800
Hello.

533
00:34:30,800 --> 00:34:31,150
Hello.

534
00:34:31,150 --> 00:34:31,520
