565
00:35:41,840 --> 00:35:43,500
Stop your nonsense. Let's go.

566
00:35:47,160 --> 00:35:48,820
You all know each other right?

567
00:35:49,920 --> 00:35:50,600
Xiaojun

568
00:35:51,280 --> 00:35:52,520
