576
00:36:04,720 --> 00:36:06,040
The wall can't stop me.

577
00:36:09,040 --> 00:36:12,320
What did you call him?

578
00:36:13,920 --> 00:36:14,640
Liangchen.

579
00:36:15,680 --> 00:36:16,520
Liangchen?

580
00:36:18,920 --> 00:36:19,240
Xiaojun

581
00:36:19,240 --> 00:36:20,480
last time at the Wintersweet...

